    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>题目大意</strong>：题目定义了一种叫做 <strong>k-回文串</strong> 的东西。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果一个串是回文串，它是 1-回文串。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "如果一个串是回文串，<strong>并且它的左半边和右半边都是</strong> $(k-1)$<strong>-回文串</strong>，那么它就是 $k$-回文串。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "给定一个长 $N \\le 5000$ 的字符串，求对于每个 $k$，字符串中有多少个子串是 $k$-回文串。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>核心转移</strong>：发现如果 <code>hui[i][j]</code> 为真，也就是 $s_{i,j}$ 为回文串，那么它的阶数就是它<strong>左半边（或右半边）的阶数 + 1</strong>。也就是 <code>dp[i][j] = dp[i][mid] + 1</code>。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "int dp[N][N];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tstring s; cin >> s;\n\tint n = s.size(); s = ' ' + s;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, 1, n)dp[i][j] = -1;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tdp[i][i] = 1;\n\t\tdp[i][i - 1] = 0;\n\t}\n\tfa(len, 2, n)fa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tint j = i + len - 1;\n\t\tif (j > n)break;\n\t\tif (dp[i + 1][j - 1] != -1 and s[i] == s[j]) {\n\t\t\tint midlen = len / 2;\n\t\t\tint mid = i + midlen - 1;\n\t\t\tif (dp[i][mid] == -1)dp[i][j] = 1;\n\t\t\telse dp[i][j] = dp[i][mid] + 1;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tvar ans = vector<int>(n + 2);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, i, n)if (dp[i][j] != -1)ans[1]++, ans[dp[i][j] + 1]--;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)ans[i] += ans[i - 1];\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cout << ans[i] << \" \\n\"[i == n];\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
